 our knowledge, Lop is the first library that allows both\nsoftware simulation and hardware realization using customized data\nrepresentations and approximate computing techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Jun 2018 21:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-05"}
