s by using TOPSIS\nmethod. We present a case study to illustrate the mechanism of the proposed\nalgorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2018 03:21:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Apr 2019 20:17:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-09"}
